Extract structured content from the Class 8 NCERT Science textbook chapter provided. Do NOT summarize or interpret. Organize the content as follows:

Hierarchy:
- Chapter Name
  - Topic Name
    - Sub-topic Header
      - Paragraphs (with page numbers)
      - Images/Diagrams (with captions and page numbers)
      - Tables (titles and page numbers)
      - Examples
      - Exercises
      - Activities
      - Questions (In-text, HOTS, Exercise)
      - External Sources or Boxed Facts

Output Format: JSON with the structure:
{
  "chapter_name": "",
  "topics": [
    {
      "topic_name": "",
      "subtopics": [
        {
          "subtopic_header": "",
          "content": {
            "paragraphs": [],
            "images": [],
            "tables": [],
            "examples": [],
            "exercises": [],
            "activities": [],
            "questions": [],
            "boxed_facts": []
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
Ensure all content includes page number and preserves textbook structure faithfully.
